---
title: Souvlaki-style Chicken with Lemony Rice and Chopped Salad
description: Succulent chicken thighs pair perfectly with our favourite puckery lemon-pepper spice blend. Fluffy rice, crunchy salad and a sprinkle of salty feta will transport your taste buds to the shores of the Mediterranean in no time!
